About
=====

A collection of routines to compute dust properties. At this stage, 
these are under active development and mainly for personal use:

Codes
=====

bhmie: a wrapper for the Bohren and Huffman subroutine. Computes scattering
       and absorption properties of distributions of spherical grains.

Downloading
===========

To download, use

git clone http://github.com/astrofrog/dust.git
cd dust
git submodule init
git submodule update

Using
=====

For instructions on installing and using, see the README files in the
different sub-directories.

Updating
========

To update, go inside the dust/ directory, and use

git pull
